subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which Rajput clan ruled Rajputana during the medieval period?
question_hi: मध्यभार में मेडियेल सेवाना के लिए किस राज्यविवादेंकोट के राज्यविभाग में किस राज्य का नाम था?
explanation_en: During the medieval period, the Kachwaha clan ruled the region that is now known as Rajputana. The kingdom's name was Rajputana, which stands for "Land of the Rulers."
